    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300038341_10_9049-9092",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "9049-9092",
      "markText": "因为上司虽有权，但意见往往不一致，未必有明确指示，更不愿意担责，一旦出了事就追究下属。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300038341&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9049&rangeEnd=9092",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2132580813ab757ag011ce2?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9049&rangeEnd=9092"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300038341_5_17625-17674",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "17625-17674",
      "markText": "可见杜凤治虽然关注世界大事和西方新事物，但他始终是从一个中国士大夫、清朝官员的角度去观察和思考的。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300038341&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=17625&rangeEnd=17674",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2132580813ab757ag011ce2?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=17625&rangeEnd=17674"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300038341_5_7739-7819",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7739-7819",
      "markText": "杜凤治又以“对扣”借了680两，实际到手340两。这些银两，说定了到任后迅速归还，通常债主会亲自或派出伙计跟随赴任官员，取得债银后回京，往返旅费也由借债者承担。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300038341&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7739&rangeEnd=7819",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2132580813ab757ag011ce2?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7739&rangeEnd=7819"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300038341_8_17459-17505",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "17459-17505",
      "markText": "瑞麟并不在乎口供是否属实，不在乎是否冤枉，只在乎口供是否符合他维护清朝在广东统治秩序的需要。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300038341&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=17459&rangeEnd=17505",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2132580813ab757ag011ce2?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=17459&rangeEnd=17505"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300038341_5_16604-16643",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "16604-16643",
      "markText": "在四会任上还曾向学官黄圣之（纪石）借阅以男同性恋为主题的“禁书”《品花宝鉴》。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300038341&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=16604&rangeEnd=16643",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2132580813ab757ag011ce2?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=16604&rangeEnd=16643"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300038341_6_4319-4564",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4319-4564",
      "markText": "不过，日记极少议论太后、皇帝、朝廷；对自己的支出记录详细，对收入则记录不多，于此等地方也可见他精明谨慎之处。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300038341&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4319&rangeEnd=4564",
